1
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:10,511
♪

2
00:00:10,611 --> 00:00:13,514
Von Stroheim: JOJO...

3
00:00:13,614 --> 00:00:16,650
I'VE HEARD SO MUCH ABOUT YOU.

4
00:00:16,683 --> 00:00:19,019
( groans )

5
00:00:19,119 --> 00:00:20,654
LISTEN, AND LISTEN GOOD.

6
00:00:20,687 --> 00:00:23,524
SANTVIENTO HERE,
THE SO‐CALLED PILLAR MAN,

7
00:00:23,624 --> 00:00:26,527
USES A MASK TO TURN MEN
INTO VAMPIRES.

8
00:00:26,593 --> 00:00:28,529
HE DOES THIS
TO MAKE THEM STRONGER,

9
00:00:28,595 --> 00:00:29,996
UND THEN HE DEVOURS THEM.

10
00:00:30,030 --> 00:00:33,634
DESTROY HIM! TAKE HIM OUT
WHILE THERE'S STILL TIME!

11
00:00:38,004 --> 00:00:40,541
Speedwagon: DON'T DO IT, JOJO!
HE'S DANGEROUS!

12
00:00:44,377 --> 00:00:45,345
JoJo: YOU'RE IT.

13
00:00:45,378 --> 00:00:46,880
( laughs )

14
00:00:49,182 --> 00:00:50,517
OH, I GET IT.

15
00:00:50,551 --> 00:00:52,719
YOU'RE ONE OF THOSE
STRONG, SILENT TYPES, RIGHT?

16
00:00:52,786 --> 00:00:55,522
EVER THOUGHT ABOUT MODELING?
YOU'VE GOT A NICE LOOK THERE.

17
00:00:55,556 --> 00:00:58,491
COME ON. LET'S SEE WHAT YOU GOT.
GIVE ME A SMILE.

18
00:00:58,559 --> 00:01:00,293
‐ ( both gasp )
‐ JoJo: I KNOW YOU CAN DO IT.

19
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:01,902
SHOW ME SOME VULNERABILITY.

20
00:01:01,968 --> 00:01:03,036
WORK WITH ME HERE.

21
00:01:03,069 --> 00:01:04,905
MAKE SOME LOVE TO THE CAMERA.

22
00:01:05,005 --> 00:01:06,072
READY? SET?

23
00:01:06,172 --> 00:01:08,308
GIVE ME HAPPY. NOW BE SILLY.

24
00:01:08,374 --> 00:01:11,077
SHOW US THOSE PEARLY WHITES.
HEH.

25
00:01:11,144 --> 00:01:13,079
♪

26
00:01:17,317 --> 00:01:19,419
( singing in Japanese )

27
00:02:44,911 --> 00:02:47,848
JoJo: COME ON, BIG GUY.
SMILE AT THE BIRDIE.

28
00:02:47,914 --> 00:02:50,316
Von Stroheim: JOJO,
STOP THIS NONSENSE IMMEDIATELY!

29
00:02:50,350 --> 00:02:51,585
Speedwagon: DON'T PROVOKE HIM.

30
00:02:51,652 --> 00:02:53,119
PLEASE, JOJO,
SANTVIENTO IS DANGEROUS.

31
00:02:53,186 --> 00:02:55,756
JoJo: YEAH, I KNOW
YOU THINK HE'S DANGEROUS,

32
00:02:55,822 --> 00:02:58,792
BUT I HAVE A THEORY
THAT MAYBE HE'S NOT SO BAD.

33
00:02:58,859 --> 00:03:00,326
LET ME TEST SOMETHING OUT HERE.

34
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:02,035
I DON'T WANT TO ASSUME HE'S EVIL

35
00:03:02,102 --> 00:03:03,937
JUST BECAUSE HE KILLED
A BUNCH OF BRAINLESS‐‐

36
00:03:04,004 --> 00:03:05,305
Von Stroheim:
WHAT ARE YOU, INSANE?!

37
00:03:05,371 --> 00:03:08,274
IF HE'S NOT EVIL,
WHY DID HE KILL ALL MY MEN?!

38
00:03:08,341 --> 00:03:10,010
JoJo: DON'T KNOW. SOME WOULD SAY

39
00:03:10,043 --> 00:03:11,712
YOU'RE RESPONSIBLE
FOR WHAT'S HAPPENED.

40
00:03:11,778 --> 00:03:13,980
WEREN'T YOU THE ONE
EXPERIMENTING ON HIM

41
00:03:14,047 --> 00:03:16,683
AND TRYING TO BLAST HIM AWAY
IN THE FIRST PLACE?

42
00:03:16,717 --> 00:03:18,351
NOT THAT I
REALLY CARE ABOUT THAT.

43
00:03:18,384 --> 00:03:21,054
THE ONLY REASON I'M HERE
TO MAKE SURE THAT SPEEDWAGON

44
00:03:21,121 --> 00:03:23,524
MAKES IT BACK TO NEW YORK
SAFE AND SOUND.

45
00:03:23,557 --> 00:03:25,959
ANYWAY, I'M NOT HERE TO FIGHT,

46
00:03:26,026 --> 00:03:27,861
AND I'M FEELING GENEROUS.

47
00:03:27,894 --> 00:03:30,196
COME ON. LOOSEN UP, BIG GUY.

48
00:03:30,230 --> 00:03:31,565
HOW 'BOUT THAT SMILE?

49
00:03:31,632 --> 00:03:33,800
( gasps )

50
00:03:33,867 --> 00:03:36,036
♪

51
00:03:37,704 --> 00:03:39,072
THAT WAS RUDE.

52
00:03:39,172 --> 00:03:41,542
HE JUST WALKED THROUGH ME
LIKE I WASN'T EVEN THERE.

53
00:03:41,575 --> 00:03:43,677
WHO THE HELL
DOES THIS GUY THINK HE IS?

54
00:03:43,744 --> 00:03:46,046
MAYBE I SHOULD TEACH HIM
A QUICK LESSON.

55
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:47,313
HAVE A NICE TRIP.

56
00:03:52,753 --> 00:03:55,221
WH‐WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT?

57
00:03:55,255 --> 00:03:58,759
THAT WAS THE WEIRDEST FEELING,
AND IT HURT.

58
00:04:05,906 --> 00:04:07,273
Santviento: WHAT IS THIS,

59
00:04:07,373 --> 00:04:08,709
THIS TOOL?

60
00:04:08,775 --> 00:04:10,611
COLD AND LONG...

61
00:04:10,677 --> 00:04:12,345
WITH MANY DIFFERENT PIECES.

62
00:04:12,412 --> 00:04:13,614
Speedwagon: HE DOES UNDERSTAND!

63
00:04:13,714 --> 00:04:15,215
HE'S NOT SIMPLY MIMICKING.

64
00:04:15,281 --> 00:04:17,951
IT TOOK HIM
PRACTICALLY NO TIME AT ALL

65
00:04:18,018 --> 00:04:19,886
TO COMPLETELY MASTER
OUR LANGUAGE.

66
00:04:23,423 --> 00:04:26,126
JoJo: HOW‐‐HOW IS HE DOING THAT?

67
00:04:26,192 --> 00:04:27,427
HE TOOK IT APART.

68
00:04:27,460 --> 00:04:30,897
HE DISMANTLED THAT ENTIRE WEAPON
LIKE SOME EXPERT GUNSMITH.

69
00:04:30,964 --> 00:04:33,133
Von Stroheim: IT TAKES A SOLDIER
DOZENS OF HOURS

70
00:04:33,233 --> 00:04:35,468
TO LEARN HOW TO FIELDSTRIP
HIS WEAPON THAT FAST.

71
00:04:35,569 --> 00:04:37,571
Speedwagon: HE'S‐‐HE'S USING
HIS ADVANCED INTELLECT

72
00:04:37,637 --> 00:04:38,805
TO LEARN EVERYTHING.

73
00:04:38,872 --> 00:04:41,407
Santviento: SO BRIGHT.

74
00:04:41,474 --> 00:04:44,077
THIS LIGHT IS NEW TO ME.

75
00:04:44,144 --> 00:04:45,378
WHAT IS IT?

76
00:04:45,445 --> 00:04:46,713
Speedwagon: DON'T YOU SEE?

77
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:48,615
WE WEREN'T THE ONES
OBSERVING ALL THIS TIME.

78
00:04:48,649 --> 00:04:51,818
HE WAS ACTUALLY WATCHING US!

79
00:04:52,786 --> 00:04:53,987
JoJo: HEY, BIG GUY,

80
00:04:54,054 --> 00:04:55,656
YOU WANNA LEARN A NEW JOKE?

81
00:04:55,722 --> 00:04:57,824
JUST STOP ME IF YOU'VE
HEARD THIS ONE BEFORE.

82
00:04:57,924 --> 00:04:59,392
KNOCK, KNOCK. KNOCK, KNOCK.

83
00:04:59,459 --> 00:05:01,968
‐ ( Von Stroheim gasps )
‐ Speedwagon: JOJO! GET AWAY!

84
00:05:03,336 --> 00:05:05,739
Santviento: YOU ARE
PLAYING GAMES, PRIMITIVE.

85
00:05:05,806 --> 00:05:08,308
I DO NOT WANT TO PLAY GAMES.

86
00:05:10,977 --> 00:05:13,013
( JoJo gasps )
WHAT THE...

87
00:05:14,447 --> 00:05:17,784
Narrator: RIB BLADES, SOMETIMES
KNOWN AS FIGHTING RIBS.

88
00:05:17,851 --> 00:05:21,087
THEY ARE CAPABLE OF BEING
MANIPULATED IN ANY DIRECTION.

89
00:05:21,154 --> 00:05:24,024
‐ Speedwagon: JOJO!
‐ ( JoJo grunting )

90
00:05:25,191 --> 00:05:27,528
( gags )

91
00:05:27,628 --> 00:05:28,762
( Santviento gasps )

92
00:05:31,865 --> 00:05:34,434
SPARKS. ENERGY.

93
00:05:34,501 --> 00:05:36,369
THIS HUMAN SEEMS...

94
00:05:36,436 --> 00:05:37,771
DIFFERENT FROM THE OTHERS.

95
00:05:37,838 --> 00:05:42,175
I WAS NOT ABLE TO ABSORB
HIS BODY INTO MINE.

96
00:05:42,208 --> 00:05:44,210
HE JUST FLEW AWAY.

97
00:05:45,546 --> 00:05:47,480
AND SOMEHOW HIS LEG,

98
00:05:47,548 --> 00:05:50,450
IT REMAINS‐‐IT STILL SEEMS FINE.

99
00:05:50,517 --> 00:05:52,553
THIS ONE IS SOMETHING NEW.

100
00:05:52,619 --> 00:05:55,288
I HAVE YET TO SEE SUCH A HUMAN.

101
00:05:55,355 --> 00:05:58,058
IS HE A UNIQUE SPECIMEN,

102
00:05:58,158 --> 00:06:01,067
OR DO ALL HUMANS
OF HIS PARTICULAR CLASS

103
00:06:01,167 --> 00:06:02,803
POSSESS THE SAME PROPERTIES?

104
00:06:02,869 --> 00:06:06,139
COULD IT BE RELATED TO AGE?

105
00:06:07,874 --> 00:06:10,577
( Speedwagon winces, screams )

106
00:06:10,644 --> 00:06:12,746
Santviento: AH, NOW I SEE.

107
00:06:12,846 --> 00:06:14,715
MY INSTINCT WAS RIGHT.

108
00:06:14,748 --> 00:06:17,083
THAT HUMAN IS UNIQUE.

109
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:19,520
Speedwagon: AGH. JOJO, PLEASE.

110
00:06:19,586 --> 00:06:21,588
MAKE IT STOP, PLEASE!

111
00:06:21,655 --> 00:06:23,757
( Von Stroheim gasping )

112
00:06:24,725 --> 00:06:26,259
JoJo: SPEEDWAGON.

113
00:06:26,359 --> 00:06:28,428
THAT BASTARD.

114
00:06:28,494 --> 00:06:30,664
LET THE OLD MAN GO, SANTVIENTO!

115
00:06:30,731 --> 00:06:32,398
NOW I'M IN THE MOOD.

116
00:06:32,432 --> 00:06:36,102
COME ON, BIG GUY.
YOU WANNA TRY AND TAKE ME ON?

117
00:06:36,169 --> 00:06:38,004
Santviento: IT WOULD SEEM

118
00:06:38,071 --> 00:06:42,576
THAT HUMANS HAVE EVOLVED
THEIR CONFIDENCE.

119
00:06:42,609 --> 00:06:43,944
( JoJo yells )

120
00:06:44,044 --> 00:06:45,946
HOPE YOU'RE HUNGRY!

121
00:06:46,046 --> 00:06:48,348
ONE HAMON SANDWICH COMING UP!

122
00:06:50,717 --> 00:06:52,786
( grunts )

123
00:06:52,886 --> 00:06:54,621
HUH? WHAT THE DEVIL?

124
00:06:54,688 --> 00:06:57,791
MY HAMON
IS MAKING THAT BLOOD FLOAT.

125
00:06:59,459 --> 00:07:01,301
SOMETHING'S WRONG HERE.

126
00:07:01,367 --> 00:07:05,205
MY HAMON IS RUNNING OFF HIM
LIKE RAIN OFF A RAINCOAT.

127
00:07:05,271 --> 00:07:06,773
HE'S SOMEHOW REPELLING IT

128
00:07:06,807 --> 00:07:08,975
AND PUSHING IT
INTO ALL OF THIS BLOOD.

129
00:07:09,075 --> 00:07:10,276
I DON'T UNDERSTAND IT.

130
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:12,946
HIS SKIN IS ACTING
LIKE A GROUND.

131
00:07:12,979 --> 00:07:16,149
SOMEHOW, IT'S BEHAVING
JUST LIKE STRAIZO'S SCARF.

132
00:07:16,249 --> 00:07:18,819
Santviento: MY BODY AND HIS BODY

133
00:07:18,885 --> 00:07:21,555
SEEM TO BE REPELLING
AGAINST ONE OTHER.

134
00:07:23,323 --> 00:07:24,825
( JoJo yelps )

135
00:07:26,326 --> 00:07:27,728
( screams )

136
00:07:27,794 --> 00:07:29,630
WHAT‐‐WHAT HAVE YOU
DONE TO MY HAND?!

137
00:07:29,663 --> 00:07:30,631
( both gasp )

138
00:07:30,664 --> 00:07:35,936
JoJo: WAIT. IT'S...

139
00:07:36,002 --> 00:07:37,771
STILL THERE.

140
00:07:37,838 --> 00:07:39,339
( both gasp )

141
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:40,340
JoJo: BUT CHECK IT OUT.

142
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,942
I CAN COMPLETELY REMOVE
MY THUMB.

143
00:07:42,008 --> 00:07:44,110
DOESN'T ANYONE HAVE
A SENSE OF HUMOR LEFT?

144
00:07:44,177 --> 00:07:46,312
COME ON, GUYS.
THIS IS FUNNY STUFF HERE.

145
00:07:46,346 --> 00:07:48,649
♪

146
00:07:48,682 --> 00:07:50,416
BUT SERIOUSLY, FOLKS.

147
00:07:50,483 --> 00:07:52,986
LUCKY THING I ROLLED
MY WRIST JUST IN TIME.

148
00:07:53,019 --> 00:07:55,355
THE BEAST'S IMMUNE TO HAMON.
( growls )

149
00:07:55,455 --> 00:07:57,323
Speedwagon:
THAT'S NOT TRUE, JOJO.

150
00:07:57,357 --> 00:07:58,258
DON'T YOU SEE?

151
00:07:58,324 --> 00:08:00,634
IT WAS HAMON
THAT WAS PROTECTING YOU.

152
00:08:00,701 --> 00:08:01,968
IT KEPT YOUR BODY

153
00:08:02,035 --> 00:08:03,804
FROM BEING COMPLETELY ABSORBED
INTO THAT THING.

154
00:08:03,870 --> 00:08:07,273
Von Stroheim: IDIOT! IT'S LIKE
EATING A BLOWFISH FOR HIM.

155
00:08:07,340 --> 00:08:09,710
HE'S KNOWS HE MUST KILL IT FIRST

156
00:08:09,810 --> 00:08:11,545
UND THEN REMOVE
THE POISON PARTS.

157
00:08:11,612 --> 00:08:15,215
THAT IS HOW SANTVIENTO PLANS
ON ABSORBING JOJO'S BODY.

158
00:08:17,551 --> 00:08:20,386
JoJo: WELL, TOO BAD FOR HIM
I'M NOT A BLOWFISH.

159
00:08:20,486 --> 00:08:23,123
REGARDLESS, I NEED TO THINK
OF SOMETHING FAST HERE.

160
00:08:23,189 --> 00:08:25,358
MAYBE IT'S TIME TO MAKE
MY EMERGENCY ESCAPE.

161
00:08:25,391 --> 00:08:27,060
Von Stroheim: YOU CAN'T DO THAT!

162
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:29,162
THE DANGER OF SANTVIENTO
ESCAPING IS TOO HIGH.

163
00:08:29,229 --> 00:08:31,665
‐ NO ONE LEAVES UNTIL HE'S DEAD!
‐ JoJo: AH, SHUT UP!

164
00:08:31,732 --> 00:08:33,967
YOU RELEASED THIS MONSTER,
AND NOW YOU'RE SAYING

165
00:08:34,034 --> 00:08:36,236
YOU NEED SOMEONE ELSE
TO CLEAN UP THE MESS?

166
00:08:36,336 --> 00:08:39,405
I DON'T NEED ANYTHING ELSE
ON MY PLATE, VON STROHEIM.

167
00:08:39,506 --> 00:08:41,908
( gasps )

168
00:08:42,008 --> 00:08:43,409
( grunts )

169
00:08:43,476 --> 00:08:46,146
LET'S SEE IF I CAN INJECT
SOME HAMON INTO HIS SYSTEM

170
00:08:46,212 --> 00:08:47,380
WITH SOMETHING SHARP.

171
00:08:49,916 --> 00:08:54,087
( gasps ) HIS SKIN
IS MALLEABLE LIKE RUBBER.

172
00:08:54,154 --> 00:08:56,489
SEE IF YOU CAN DODGE THIS ONE,
BIG GUY!

173
00:08:56,557 --> 00:08:59,225
HOW ABOUT A DOSE OF HAMON
RIGHT IN THE EYE?!

174
00:08:59,259 --> 00:09:01,935
I HOPE YOU'RE READY
FOR YOUR CAN'T‐MISS CLOSE‐UP.

175
00:09:04,838 --> 00:09:06,673
WHAT? THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

176
00:09:06,740 --> 00:09:09,209
EVEN HIS EYES FEEL LIKE
THEY'RE SOME KIND OF RUBBER.

177
00:09:09,275 --> 00:09:11,612
Speedwagon: JOJO,
GET OUT OF THERE RIGHT NOW!

178
00:09:11,678 --> 00:09:14,881
( JoJo gasps, groans )

179
00:09:14,948 --> 00:09:16,116
Speedwagon: JOJO!

180
00:09:16,182 --> 00:09:18,118
Von Stroheim: THAT HIT
TO THE SOLAR PLEXUS

181
00:09:18,184 --> 00:09:20,086
COMPLETELY KNOCKED
THE WIND OUT OF HIM.

182
00:09:20,954 --> 00:09:22,789
Santviento: HMM.

183
00:09:22,856 --> 00:09:25,926
HE SEEMS TO CREATE
HIS OWN ENERGY.

184
00:09:25,959 --> 00:09:28,261
HE CONTROLS IT
WITH HIS BREATHING.

185
00:09:28,294 --> 00:09:31,464
BUT LYING THERE NOW UNCONSCIOUS,

186
00:09:31,565 --> 00:09:34,801
HE IS AS VULNERABLE
AS ANY OTHER HUMAN.

187
00:09:34,901 --> 00:09:38,605
Speedwagon: JOJO! YOU'VE GOT
TO USE YOUR HAMON BREATHING!

188
00:09:39,806 --> 00:09:41,975
‐ ( crack )
‐ ( screams )

189
00:09:42,075 --> 00:09:44,545
YOU'VE GOT TO BREATHE! OHH!

190
00:09:44,611 --> 00:09:49,149
USE YOUR HAMON BREATHING!
BREATHE, DAMN IT! BREATHE!

191
00:09:49,249 --> 00:09:50,817
Von Stroheim: NO,
THERE'S NO STOPPING HIM.

192
00:09:50,884 --> 00:09:54,788
I'VE GOT TO INITIATE
THE SELF‐DESTRUCT SEQUENCE.

193
00:09:54,821 --> 00:09:56,990
( breathing heavily )

194
00:10:00,433 --> 00:10:02,536
FOR THE FATHERLAND

195
00:10:02,603 --> 00:10:04,437
UND FOR ETERNAL GLO‐‐

196
00:10:04,538 --> 00:10:07,173
JoJo: I WOULDN'T DO THAT
IF I WERE YOU.

197
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:09,342
EVERYONE JUST CALM DOWN HERE.

198
00:10:09,409 --> 00:10:11,444
LOOKS LIKE MY GAMBLE PAID OFF.

199
00:10:11,545 --> 00:10:13,847
FIGURING THAT ATTACKS
FROM OUTSIDE ARE NO GOOD,

200
00:10:13,914 --> 00:10:16,016
I'M GOING TO SEND
SOME HAMON INTO HIM

201
00:10:16,082 --> 00:10:17,684
WHILE HE TRIES
TO ENJOY HIS MEAL.

202
00:10:17,751 --> 00:10:18,952
Speedwagon: JOJO!

203
00:10:19,019 --> 00:10:21,922
JoJo: I WAITED FOR YOU
TO START DEVOURING ME.

204
00:10:21,955 --> 00:10:23,590
THIS IS GONNA BE FUN.

205
00:10:23,624 --> 00:10:25,592
ENJOY YOUR HAMON BLAST!

206
00:10:35,736 --> 00:10:38,471
♪

207
00:10:42,743 --> 00:10:45,712
( JoJo panting )

208
00:10:45,779 --> 00:10:47,280
I‐‐I THINK I GET IT.

209
00:10:47,313 --> 00:10:50,551
NOW THAT I'VE SEEN HIM
FROM THE INSIDE, I UNDERSTAND.

210
00:10:50,617 --> 00:10:53,153
HIS WHOLE BODY
IS ONE BIG DIGESTIVE SYSTEM.

211
00:10:53,219 --> 00:10:54,655
EVERY ONE OF HIS CELLS,

212
00:10:54,755 --> 00:10:57,257
THEY'RE ALL FILLED WITH
AGGRESSIVE DIGESTIVE ENZYMES,

213
00:10:57,323 --> 00:10:59,492
MAKING IT POSSIBLE
TO DISSOLVE HIS PREY.

214
00:10:59,593 --> 00:11:01,668
IT LOOKS LIKE
HE'S ABSORBING THEM,

215
00:11:01,768 --> 00:11:04,337
WHEN ACTUALLY
HE'S DIGESTING THEM WHOLE.

216
00:11:04,404 --> 00:11:07,574
HAMON. THAT WAS WHAT
KEPT ME FROM BEING DIGESTED.

217
00:11:07,641 --> 00:11:11,077
I SENT IT INSIDE HIM
WHEN HE TRIED TO EAT ME.

218
00:11:11,144 --> 00:11:12,813
Speedwagon: JOJO,
YOUR HAMON WASN'T ENOUGH.

219
00:11:12,846 --> 00:11:16,082
YOU HAVE TO FIND A WAY TO
COMPLETELY DESTROY SANTVIENTO.

220
00:11:16,149 --> 00:11:17,117
( gasps )

221
00:11:17,183 --> 00:11:18,484
( Santviento grunts )

222
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:20,153
♪

223
00:11:28,494 --> 00:11:30,531
JoJo: THE SEPARATED PARTS
OF SANTVIENTO

224
00:11:30,631 --> 00:11:32,633
ARE TRYING TO CONNECT
TO ONE ANOTHER.

225
00:11:32,699 --> 00:11:35,201
THAT'S PRETTY MUCH EXACTLY
WHAT HAPPENED WITH STRAIZO.

226
00:11:35,268 --> 00:11:37,804
LUCKY ME, I FIGURED
YOU WOULD TRY TO GO

227
00:11:37,871 --> 00:11:39,439
AND DO THE SAME THING.

228
00:11:39,506 --> 00:11:40,206
VON STROHEIM!

229
00:11:40,306 --> 00:11:42,442
( Von Stroheim shuddering )

230
00:11:44,545 --> 00:11:45,378
AAH!

231
00:11:45,478 --> 00:11:47,881
JoJo: COME ON!
GET AHOLD OF YOURSELF!

232
00:11:47,948 --> 00:11:49,716
DOES THIS THING
HAVE ANY WEAKNESSES?

233
00:11:49,816 --> 00:11:52,218
Von Stroheim: UH, SUNLIGHT!
JA, THAT'S IT.

234
00:11:52,285 --> 00:11:55,055
IT WAS THERE ON THE WALLS
OF THE CAVE.

235
00:11:55,155 --> 00:11:56,557
SUNLIGHT IS HIS NATURAL ENEMY.

236
00:11:56,657 --> 00:12:00,060
THE VERY REASON HE MADE
THE MASKS IN THE FIRST PLACE

237
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:01,535
WAS TO CONQUER THE SUN.

238
00:12:01,568 --> 00:12:03,236
JoJo: HMM.

239
00:12:06,807 --> 00:12:07,741
( grunts )

240
00:12:09,175 --> 00:12:10,877
Von Stroheim: ARE YOU INSANE?!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

241
00:12:10,911 --> 00:12:15,215
YOU CAN'T LET SANTVIENTO
ESCAPE INTO THE OUTSIDE WORLD!

242
00:12:15,248 --> 00:12:16,517
JoJo: ON THE CONTRARY,

243
00:12:16,583 --> 00:12:20,420
I THINK HE NEEDS TO GO
ON A NICE SUNLIT STROLL.

244
00:12:20,521 --> 00:12:23,590
( grunting )

245
00:12:23,690 --> 00:12:25,592
Speedwagon:
HE'S RUNNING OUT OF BREATH.

246
00:12:25,692 --> 00:12:28,194
HE WON'T BE ABLE
TO CONTROL HIS HAMON.

247
00:12:28,261 --> 00:12:30,263
HE HASN'T HAD
ENOUGH TRAINING WITH IT.

248
00:12:30,363 --> 00:12:33,166
THIS FIGHT HAS
COMPLETELY EXHAUSTED HIM.

249
00:12:33,233 --> 00:12:35,602
Santviento:
CEASE THIS FOOLISHNESS NOW,

250
00:12:35,669 --> 00:12:37,838
YOU LOWLY PRIMITIVE.

251
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,542
( yells )

252
00:12:43,243 --> 00:12:44,911
‐ ( JoJo gasps )
‐ ( Santviento chuckles )

253
00:12:44,945 --> 00:12:48,782
Speedwagon: REMEMBER, YOU MUST
CONTROL YOUR HAMON BREATHING!

254
00:12:48,882 --> 00:12:50,250
JoJo: IF I COULD BREATHE,

255
00:12:50,283 --> 00:12:52,586
I PROBABLY WOULDN'T BE
SO TIRED IN THE FIRST PLACE.

256
00:12:52,619 --> 00:12:53,787
COME ON, BIG GUY.

257
00:12:53,854 --> 00:12:56,957
I THINK WE'VE ALL HAD
JUST ABOUT ENOUGH OF YOU.

258
00:12:57,023 --> 00:13:00,293
BUT FORTUNATELY FOR ME,
WE'RE JUST A FEW STEPS AWAY

259
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:03,136
FROM THE TWO OF US
CATCHING SOME NICE RAYS.

260
00:13:03,236 --> 00:13:05,371
( grunting )

261
00:13:07,307 --> 00:13:08,742
‐ ( thump )
‐ ( gasps )

262
00:13:08,809 --> 00:13:10,276
WHAT THE HELL?

263
00:13:10,310 --> 00:13:11,311
( crackling )

264
00:13:11,411 --> 00:13:13,647
I CAN'T MOVE.

265
00:13:13,714 --> 00:13:15,315
I FEEL SO HEAVY.

266
00:13:15,415 --> 00:13:18,318
WHAT‐‐WHAT'S HAPPENING TO ME?

267
00:13:19,452 --> 00:13:20,453
Narrator: MEAT INVADE,

268
00:13:20,486 --> 00:13:23,156
ALSO KNOWN AS FOUL FLESH.

269
00:13:23,223 --> 00:13:26,392
JoJo: THEY'RE PIECES
OF HIS FLESH.

270
00:13:26,459 --> 00:13:29,495
THEY'RE‐‐THEY'RE FEEDING ON ME.

271
00:13:29,563 --> 00:13:32,666
( groans ) YOU‐‐YOU SON OF A‐‐

272
00:13:32,766 --> 00:13:33,900
( groans )

273
00:13:33,967 --> 00:13:35,502
GOT TO STAY FOCUSED.

274
00:13:35,569 --> 00:13:38,972
Santviento: I NEVER ONCE
IMAGINED A HUMAN SUCH AS YOU

275
00:13:39,005 --> 00:13:41,307
WOULD BE BORN
DURING MY SLUMBER.

276
00:13:41,341 --> 00:13:44,277
( Von Stroheim gasping )

277
00:13:44,344 --> 00:13:45,579
( Speedwagon gasps )

278
00:13:45,646 --> 00:13:47,581
♪

279
00:13:47,648 --> 00:13:48,582
WHAT?

280
00:13:58,692 --> 00:14:01,367
Von Stroheim: JOESTAR,
LEAVE THE REST TO ME,

281
00:14:01,434 --> 00:14:02,669
COLONEL RUDOL VON STROHEIM.

282
00:14:02,703 --> 00:14:05,305
OPENING THE DOOR
WILL END ALL THIS.

283
00:14:05,371 --> 00:14:08,308
ALLOW ME TO HELP YOU DESTROY
THIS VILE CREATURE.

284
00:14:08,374 --> 00:14:10,443
JoJo: WOW, VON STROHEIM.

285
00:14:10,511 --> 00:14:12,145
I WOULD HAVE NEVER THOUGHT...

286
00:14:12,212 --> 00:14:13,479
( cracking )

287
00:14:13,547 --> 00:14:17,217
Santviento: HUMPH.
WELL ATTEMPTED, PRIMITIVES.

288
00:14:19,853 --> 00:14:21,955
( Von Stroheim screaming )

289
00:14:25,992 --> 00:14:28,562
I CAN ALMOST REACH THE DOOR.

290
00:14:28,662 --> 00:14:30,531
( groaning )

291
00:14:30,564 --> 00:14:34,000
Santviento:
A MEANINGLESS STRUGGLE. HUMPH.

292
00:14:35,468 --> 00:14:37,403
( Von Stroheim screams )

293
00:14:37,470 --> 00:14:39,506
JoJo: THIS IS BAD.

294
00:14:39,573 --> 00:14:40,707
Von Stroheim: JOESTAR, GET UP.

295
00:14:40,741 --> 00:14:43,243
DON'T JUST LIE THERE
LIKE A BABY.

296
00:14:43,309 --> 00:14:44,745
JoJo: I'M TRYING TO THINK HERE.

297
00:14:44,811 --> 00:14:47,413
IF YOU HADN'T NOTICED,
WE'RE BOTH IN DEEP TROUBLE.

298
00:14:47,514 --> 00:14:48,915
Von Stroheim: SILENCE!

299
00:14:49,015 --> 00:14:52,152
DO YOU SEE THOSE AXES
ON THE WALL NEXT TO YOU?

300
00:14:52,218 --> 00:14:53,353
REACH UP, UND GRAB ONE.

301
00:14:53,419 --> 00:14:55,656
TAKE ONE, UND CHOP OFF MY LEG!

302
00:14:55,722 --> 00:14:57,423
JoJo: I‐‐I CAN'T DO THAT!

303
00:14:57,524 --> 00:14:59,425
Von Stroheim: YOU COWARD,
CUT OFF MY LEG.

304
00:14:59,526 --> 00:15:01,702
IT'S THE ONLY WAY
WE'RE GETTING THAT DOOR OPEN.

305
00:15:01,768 --> 00:15:04,437
JoJo: MAYBE YOU'RE RIGHT,
BUT ARE YOU SURE ABOUT THIS?

306
00:15:04,538 --> 00:15:07,073
I MEAN, THERE HAS GOT TO BE
SOME OTHER WAY.

307
00:15:07,107 --> 00:15:08,441
Von Stroheim: DO AS I SAY!

308
00:15:08,542 --> 00:15:10,911
HE'S RECOVERING, JOESTAR.

309
00:15:10,944 --> 00:15:12,212
JoJo: BUT I'M NO DOCTOR.

310
00:15:12,278 --> 00:15:14,380
I'VE NO IDEA
HOW TO DO THIS RIGHT.

311
00:15:14,447 --> 00:15:16,449
Von Stroheim:
I AM A PROUD SERVANT

312
00:15:16,517 --> 00:15:18,719
OF THE WEHRMACHT!
I AM PREPARED TO DO

313
00:15:18,785 --> 00:15:20,954
WHATEVER IS REQUIRED
TO FULFILL MY DUTY!

314
00:15:21,021 --> 00:15:24,124
I PROUDLY GIVE UP MY LEG
FOR THE FATHERLAND!

315
00:15:24,224 --> 00:15:26,359
NOW HURRY UP
BEFORE IT'S TOO LATE!

316
00:15:26,426 --> 00:15:29,763
DAMN IT! DO IT NOW, JOESTAR!

317
00:15:31,431 --> 00:15:33,066
JoJo: OKAY, I'LL DO IT.

318
00:15:33,133 --> 00:15:36,402
IF YOU REALLY WANT ME TO
CHOP IT OFF, THEN OFF IT GOES.

319
00:15:36,469 --> 00:15:38,772
Von Stroheim: I DEMAND
THAT YOU CHOP IT OFF NOW!

320
00:15:38,805 --> 00:15:42,375
JoJo: I FIGURED THIS GUY WAS
JUST SOME BLOATED POWERMONGER,

321
00:15:42,442 --> 00:15:45,546
BUT I GOTTA HAND IT TO HIM.
HE'S GOT GUTS.

322
00:15:45,612 --> 00:15:47,714
I WISH THERE WERE
SOME OTHER WAY.

323
00:15:47,781 --> 00:15:50,216
BUT IF HE'S
COURAGEOUS ENOUGH, THEN...

324
00:15:50,283 --> 00:15:53,620
FORGIVE ME! ( yells )

325
00:15:53,654 --> 00:15:55,822
( Von Stroheim gasping )

326
00:15:57,323 --> 00:16:01,334
( yells )

327
00:16:03,403 --> 00:16:06,507
( Santviento gasps )

328
00:16:09,409 --> 00:16:11,512
( screaming )

329
00:16:15,682 --> 00:16:19,185
JoJo: TELL ME, BIG GUY, HOW DOES
THAT SUNSHINE FEEL ON YOUR SKIN?

330
00:16:19,252 --> 00:16:21,354
( Santviento screaming )

331
00:16:23,023 --> 00:16:24,658
Von Stroheim: WE DID IT.

332
00:16:28,795 --> 00:16:32,332
( cracking )

333
00:16:32,365 --> 00:16:33,867
JoJo: WHAT'S HE DOING?

334
00:16:33,967 --> 00:16:35,536
( gasps )

335
00:16:35,636 --> 00:16:37,137
( Von Stroheim screams )

336
00:16:37,203 --> 00:16:38,438
HELP ME!

337
00:16:38,505 --> 00:16:41,207
THAT MONSTER IS TRYING
TO CRAWL INSIDE MY LEG!

338
00:16:41,274 --> 00:16:42,676
JoJo: GET OUTTA THERE, YOU!

339
00:16:45,045 --> 00:16:46,980
WHOA. THIS IS A SHOCK.

340
00:16:47,047 --> 00:16:50,383
VON STROHEIM'S BASICALLY OKAY,
AND HE'S FREE OF ANY HAMON.

341
00:16:50,450 --> 00:16:51,384
‐ ( thump )
‐ HUH?

342
00:16:51,484 --> 00:16:53,554
( Von Stroheim gasping )

343
00:16:56,456 --> 00:16:59,826
DAMN IT, YOU GET OUT OF ME,
SANTVIENTO!

344
00:16:59,893 --> 00:17:02,736
JoJo: I‐‐I CAN'T BELIEVE
THIS THING'S WILLPOWER.

345
00:17:02,836 --> 00:17:05,071
I'VE NEVER SEEN
ANYTHING LIKE IT.

346
00:17:07,173 --> 00:17:08,809
IF HE STAYS INSIDE VON STROHEIM,

347
00:17:08,875 --> 00:17:11,645
HE'LL BE TOTALLY FINE
EVEN HERE IN BROAD DAYLIGHT.

348
00:17:11,712 --> 00:17:13,547
Von Stroheim: I CAN FEEL HIM.

349
00:17:13,580 --> 00:17:15,081
THIS CAN'T BE REAL.

350
00:17:15,148 --> 00:17:18,484
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW WHAT
THE WORST PART ABOUT THIS IS?

351
00:17:18,552 --> 00:17:21,254
MY LEG DOESN'T
EVEN HURT ANYMORE.

352
00:17:21,321 --> 00:17:23,890
IT FEELS PLEASANT.
YOU BELIEVE THAT?

353
00:17:23,924 --> 00:17:26,259
‐ ( groaning )
‐ JoJo: MY GOD.

354
00:17:26,359 --> 00:17:27,360
VON STROHEIM!

355
00:17:27,427 --> 00:17:31,064
♪

356
00:17:31,097 --> 00:17:32,566
( gasps )

357
00:17:32,599 --> 00:17:36,670
( Von Stroheim groaning )

358
00:17:40,607 --> 00:17:43,577
JoJo: WAIT. WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

359
00:17:43,610 --> 00:17:45,345
PUT IT DOWN, VON STROHEIM.

360
00:17:45,411 --> 00:17:47,781
Von Stroheim: STAY BACK!

361
00:17:47,848 --> 00:17:51,585
YOU'VE SEEN WHAT HORRIBLE THINGS
SANTVIENTO IS CAPABLE OF!

362
00:17:51,618 --> 00:17:53,286
THERE IS NO HOPE!

363
00:17:53,386 --> 00:17:55,455
MY DESTINY HAS BEEN DETERMINED!

364
00:17:55,556 --> 00:18:00,360
SO NOW ALL I CAN DO
IS DESTROY THE BOTH OF US!

365
00:18:00,426 --> 00:18:04,971
BUT I HAVE ONE MORE THING TO SAY
TO YOU BEFORE MY TIME IS DONE.

366
00:18:05,038 --> 00:18:08,975
IF YOU KNOW WHAT'S GOOD FOR YOU,
YOU LISTEN CLOSE, ENGLISHMAN.

367
00:18:09,075 --> 00:18:12,245
OUR WEHRMACHT, WE‐‐
WE DID NOT AWAKEN SANTVIENTO

368
00:18:12,312 --> 00:18:16,617
SIMPLY FOR SCIENTIFIC RESEARCH
OR MILITARY GAIN.

369
00:18:16,650 --> 00:18:17,618
JoJo: THEN WHY?

370
00:18:17,651 --> 00:18:19,886
WHY DID YOU RISK IT? TELL ME!

371
00:18:19,953 --> 00:18:21,888
Von Stroheim: SILENCE!
IT'S YOUR DESTINY

372
00:18:21,955 --> 00:18:24,625
TO HEAR THESE WORDS
FROM MY LIPS, JOESTAR!

373
00:18:24,658 --> 00:18:27,160
SANTVIENTO IS JUST
THE TIP OF THE ICEBERG.

374
00:18:27,227 --> 00:18:30,230
THE WEHRMACHT HAS DISCOVERED
ANOTHER PILLAR IN EUROPE. AGH!

375
00:18:30,296 --> 00:18:31,665
WE NOW KNOW THAT SANTVIENTO

376
00:18:31,732 --> 00:18:34,434
IS NOT THE ONLY ONE
OF HIS KIND AROUND.

377
00:18:34,500 --> 00:18:36,002
( gasps, screams )

378
00:18:36,102 --> 00:18:38,004
JoJo: WAIT.
SO THERE'S MORE OF THEM?!

379
00:18:38,071 --> 00:18:40,440
WHERE ARE THEY?
TELL ME, VON STROHEIM! WHERE?

380
00:18:40,507 --> 00:18:41,808
Von Stroheim: I'M SORRY,

381
00:18:41,842 --> 00:18:44,310
BUT I DON'T HAVE THAT ANSWER
FOR YOU, JOESTAR.

382
00:18:44,344 --> 00:18:45,979
THERE ARE
MORE PILLAR MEN OUT THERE,

383
00:18:46,012 --> 00:18:48,949
UND THEY HAVE POWERS THAT ARE
BEYOND OUR WILDEST IMAGINATION.

384
00:18:49,015 --> 00:18:51,184
FOR MILLENNIA, THOSE POWERS
HAVE REMAINED DORMANT,

385
00:18:51,251 --> 00:18:54,187
BUT THAT WON'T LAST,
UND SOON THEY WILL AWAKEN.

386
00:18:54,254 --> 00:18:57,190
YOU MUST FIND ANOTHER WEAKNESS
OTHER THAN JUST SUNLIGHT,

387
00:18:57,290 --> 00:18:59,192
OR ELSE HOPE IS LOST.

388
00:18:59,292 --> 00:19:02,035
THAT'S WHY WE WERE
EXPERIMENTING ON SANTVIENTO.

389
00:19:02,102 --> 00:19:04,037
WE WERE LOOKING
FOR THAT WEAKNESS.

390
00:19:04,104 --> 00:19:07,173
THERE'S A BATTLE AGAINST
THE PILLAR MEN YET TO BE FOUGHT.

391
00:19:07,207 --> 00:19:10,677
THE EVENTS OF 50 YEARS AGO
CALL UPON YOU FOR THAT BATTLE.

392
00:19:10,711 --> 00:19:12,145
LISTEN TO ME.

393
00:19:12,212 --> 00:19:15,649
YOU WILL NEED MORE THAN JUST
YOUR HAMON TO OVERCOME THEM.

394
00:19:15,716 --> 00:19:17,684
YOU MUST GO TO ROME!

395
00:19:17,718 --> 00:19:19,953
THERE YOU WILL FIND
SOMEONE WHO CAN HELP YOU!

396
00:19:20,020 --> 00:19:24,157
IT IS SOMEONE THAT
YOUR SPEEDWAGON KNOWS VERY WELL.

397
00:19:24,224 --> 00:19:26,059
( grunts )

398
00:19:26,126 --> 00:19:29,663
SANTVIENTO IS
TRYING TO MOVE MY BODY

399
00:19:29,730 --> 00:19:32,232
INTO THAT WELL
SO HE CAN HIDE AGAIN.

400
00:19:32,298 --> 00:19:35,869
BUT HE CAN'T STOP ME FROM
OPENING UP MY BODY COMPLETELY

401
00:19:35,902 --> 00:19:38,038
TO LET THE SUN SHINE IN.

402
00:19:39,506 --> 00:19:41,207
( spits )

403
00:19:42,509 --> 00:19:43,677
JoJo: VON STROHEIM...

404
00:19:43,744 --> 00:19:45,912
DON'T YOU DARE.

405
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:48,381
( Von Stroheim laughs )

406
00:19:48,414 --> 00:19:49,883
"HUMAN GREATNESS LIES

407
00:19:49,916 --> 00:19:52,886
IN HAVING THE COURAGE
TO FACE DOWN ONE'S FEARS."

408
00:19:52,919 --> 00:19:55,221
DO YOU KNOW WHO SAID THAT?

409
00:19:55,255 --> 00:19:56,489
THE GREEK HISTORIAN PLUTARCH.

410
00:19:56,557 --> 00:19:58,191
( JoJo gasps )

411
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:01,768
Von Stroheim: FAREWELL...

412
00:20:01,835 --> 00:20:03,770
YOU ANNOYING ENGLISHMAN!

413
00:20:03,837 --> 00:20:05,038
JoJo: DON'T DO IT!

414
00:20:05,138 --> 00:20:08,008
I STILL HAVE QUESTIONS FOR YOU!
VON STROHEIM!

415
00:20:10,043 --> 00:20:11,177
( groans )

416
00:20:11,211 --> 00:20:14,180
DAMN THAT CRAZY GERMAN
AND ALL HIS HONOR.

417
00:20:14,214 --> 00:20:15,716
( groans )

418
00:20:15,816 --> 00:20:18,952
I'M SURE THAT WE COULD HAVE
FOUND ANOTHER WAY.

419
00:20:19,019 --> 00:20:20,020
( sighs )

420
00:20:20,053 --> 00:20:21,021
( gasps )

421
00:20:21,054 --> 00:20:23,023
♪

422
00:20:25,058 --> 00:20:26,527
( gasps )

423
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:28,729
( cracking )

424
00:20:32,065 --> 00:20:35,401
SANTVIENTO!

425
00:20:35,468 --> 00:20:38,304
Santviento:
YOU ANNOY ME, PRIMITIVE.

426
00:20:38,371 --> 00:20:40,240
I WILL DESTROY YOU!

427
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:41,808
JoJo: STEADY YOUR BREATHING.

428
00:20:41,875 --> 00:20:43,710
USE YOUR HAMON TECHNIQUE.

429
00:20:43,744 --> 00:20:45,646
( deep breaths )

430
00:20:45,712 --> 00:20:47,648
( Santviento growls )

431
00:20:47,714 --> 00:20:49,816
( JoJo growls )

432
00:20:54,154 --> 00:20:56,757
( screams )

433
00:20:57,824 --> 00:21:00,694
Santviento: PRIMITIVE,
WHY OPPOSE ME?

434
00:21:00,761 --> 00:21:03,169
YOU WERE DOOMED HERE
FROM THE START.

435
00:21:03,236 --> 00:21:04,270
JoJo: HAH!

436
00:21:04,337 --> 00:21:06,372
I KNOW JUST WHAT
YOU'RE GOING TO SAY NEXT.

437
00:21:06,439 --> 00:21:08,374
YOU'LL SAY, "I'VE SEEN
RIGHT THROUGH YOU

438
00:21:08,441 --> 00:21:09,610
ALL THIS TIME, JOESTAR."

439
00:21:09,710 --> 00:21:11,044
Santviento:
I'VE SEEN RIGHT THROUGH YOU

440
00:21:11,111 --> 00:21:13,246
ALL THIS TIME, JOESTAR.
( gasps )

441
00:21:15,716 --> 00:21:18,619
( screams )

442
00:21:18,685 --> 00:21:20,621
JoJo: IT'S HIGH NOON
OVER THIS WELL.

443
00:21:20,687 --> 00:21:22,623
THE SUN REFLECTING
OFF OF THE WATER

444
00:21:22,689 --> 00:21:23,857
SHOULD COOK YOU NICELY,

445
00:21:23,924 --> 00:21:26,026
ALTHOUGH I DOUBT
YOU EVEN THOUGHT OF THAT.

446
00:21:26,092 --> 00:21:29,395
YOU WERE THINKING ABOUT JUMPING
UNDER THE NICE COOL WATER

447
00:21:29,462 --> 00:21:31,598
AND GETTING
OUT OF THE SUN, RIGHT?

448
00:21:31,632 --> 00:21:33,399
( deep breath )

449
00:21:33,466 --> 00:21:35,802
WELL, SCREW THAT IDEA.

450
00:21:35,869 --> 00:21:38,271
I'M NOT LETTING YOU
TOUCH THE WATER!

451
00:21:38,304 --> 00:21:39,472
( grunting )

452
00:21:39,540 --> 00:21:42,475
( screams )

453
00:21:42,576 --> 00:21:44,377
♪

454
00:21:52,653 --> 00:21:54,721
( JoJo sighs )

455
00:21:56,056 --> 00:21:58,959
I'M ALIVE, THANKS TO THE SUN.

456
00:21:58,992 --> 00:22:01,067
HE'S A STATUE NOW.

457
00:22:01,134 --> 00:22:04,905
BUT WE FINALLY GOT THAT SMILE.

458
00:22:04,971 --> 00:22:06,907
♪

459
00:22:22,523 --> 00:22:25,759
♪ I'LL BE THE ROUNDABOUT

460
00:22:25,826 --> 00:22:29,596
♪ THE WORDS
WILL MAKE YOU OUT AND OUT ♪

461
00:22:29,663 --> 00:22:34,868
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

462
00:22:34,968 --> 00:22:37,370
♪ CALL IT MORNING
DRIVING THROUGH THE SOUND ♪

463
00:22:37,470 --> 00:22:42,308
♪ AND IN AND OUT THE VALLEY

464
00:22:49,550 --> 00:22:52,886
♪ THE MUSIC DANCE AND SING

465
00:22:52,953 --> 00:22:56,557
♪ THEY MAKE THE CHILDREN
REALLY RING ♪

466
00:22:56,657 --> 00:23:01,868
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

467
